		{
			description: [
				"&2&lAge I Â· The Sieve.&r"
				""
				"You have a tree, a block of dirt, and a whole lot of nothing. By the end of this Age you will have turned that nothing into metal, machines, and the first automated forge in the sky."
				""
				"Follow the line left to right. The branches below teach mesh upgrades and the two crystals that open every tech mod."
