		{
			dependencies: ["2101000000000006"]
			description: [
				"Breaking cobble by hand got you this far. Now stop."
				""
				"A &eCobble Gen Tier1&r is a block that just... makes cobblestone, into its own buffer. Hopper it out, pipe it away, walk off. It never stops."
				""
				"&7Recipe: 6 logs around a &eGlass&r, with a &eWater Bucket&r and a &eLava Bucket&r either side.&r"
				""
				"&cIt eats both buckets&r - but you can bucket your lava source back up out of your cobble generator first. That is why this waits until you have iron."
				""
				"&eFive tiers&r, each faster than the last: &7logs &8→&r cobble &8→&r iron &8→&r gold &8→&r diamond&r. Upgrade when the buffer can't keep up."
				""
				"&8Feeds straight into hammers, sieves, and eventually your ME system. Cobble is the bottom of every chain in this pack - automate it early."
			]
			icon: "cobblefordays:tier_1"
			id: "0AC0000000000002"
